If you use PTB, try the following to listen to scaner.
1. find out the serial port name by using findingSerialPort.m
2. change the scaner box to a mode in which you listen to the port directly.
   in this case, switch to "Presentation" mode
3. change in the mainexp.m correspondingly in %% Prep Port
4. change the BaudRate to 19200
5. find out the number represents trigger by print the pluse in the command window
